				\begin{document}
$$ \mathrm{Copies}/\mu \mathrm{L}\kern0.28em =\kern0.28em \left(\mathrm{ng}/\mu \mathrm{L}\times {10}^9\right)/\left(\mathrm{M}\mathrm{W}\kern0.28em \mathrm{of}\kern0.28em \mathrm{transcripts}\right)\times \left(6.023\times {10}^{23}\right). $$
\end{document}Copies/μL=(ng/μL×109)/(MWoftranscripts)×(6.023×1023).
